OL,3,CLabour braced for big losses in London
OL,4,Celection count
OL,6,FLabour is bracing itself for big
OL,7,Flosses as counting gets underway in
OL,8,Fthe London borough council elections.
OL,10,FOpinion polls ahead of yesterday's
OL,11,Felection predicted a Green Party surge
OL,12,Fin previously rock-solid Labour areas.
OL,14,FLondon Assembly Green Party member Zoe
OL,15,FGarbett is hoping to oust Labour's
OL,16,FCaroline Woodley as Hackney mayor.
OL,18,FLabour is also expected to face a
OL,19,Fstrong challenge in Enfield,
OL,20,FIslington, Lambeth, Lewisham and
OL,21,FNewham.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
