OL,3,CLabour braced for big losses in London
OL,4,Celection count
OL,6,FThe Conservatives London campaign
OL,7,Ffocussed on trying to win back three
OL,8,Fcouncils lost to Labour in 2022 -
OL,9,FBarnet, Wandsworth and Westminster.
OL,11,FBut Kemi Badenoch's party is facing a
OL,12,Fchallenge from Reform UK in outer
OL,13,FLondon boroughs including Bexley,
OL,14,FBromley and Hillingdon.
OL,16,FReform's main London target is
OL,17,FHavering currently run by a coalition
OL,18,Fof residents' associations.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
