OL,3,CLabour braced for big losses in London
OL,4,Celection count
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats who control a
OL,7,Ftrio of southwest London boroughs -
OL,8,FKingston, Richmond and Sutton - are
OL,9,Fhoping to add Labour-run Merton.
